{{zh-hanzi|[[行]][[不]][[改]][[名]]，[[坐]][[不]][[改]][[姓]]}}
==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: xíng bù găi míng, zuò bù găi xìng
===Etymology===
Literally: to not change your given name after doing something, and not change your surname after sitting down
===Idiom===
#  to do things in an aboveboard and straightforward manner
# to have nothing to hide
#: ''[[我]]'''行不改名，坐不改姓'''，[[要是]][[有]][[什麼]][[問題]]，[[叫]][[他]][[直接]][[來]][[找]][[我]]。''
#: ''[[我]]'''行不改名，坐不改姓'''，[[要是]][[有]][[什么]][[问题]]，[[叫]][[他]][[直接]][[来]][[找]][[我]]。 ''
#: ''I '''have nothing to hide'''; if he has a problem, tell him to come see me directly.''
